## Flags Summary

| Flag | Location | Method |
|---|---|---|
| Flag 1 | `/var/www/flag1.txt` | Initial shell via Drupalgeddon2 |
| Flag 2 | `/var/www/sites/default/settings.php` | Config file enumeration |
| Flag 3 | Drupal content page (as admin) | MySQL password reset ‚Üí Drupal login |
| Flag 4 | `/home/flag4/flag4.txt` | Shell enumeration |
| Final Flag | `/root/thefinalflag.txt` | SUID find ‚Üí root shell |

